## Architettura MCP multi-database

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "LAYER 1 - DBA / Client"
        DBA[DBA<br/>VS Code + Cline]
        CLIENT[Client MCP]
    end
    
    subgraph "LAYER 2 - AI Orchestration"
        LLM[LLM Provider<br/>Claude API / Azure OpenAI / Bedrock]
    end
    
    subgraph "LAYER 3 - MCP Servers<br/>Data Access Layer"
        SQLCL[SQLcl MCP Server<br/>Oracle]
        MSSQL[SQL Server MCP]
        PG[PostgreSQL MCP]
        MYSQL[MySQL MCP]
    end
    
    subgraph "LAYER 4 - Database"
        ORACLE[Oracle CDB/PDB<br/>Prod/Test/Dev]
        SQLSERV[SQL Server<br/>Prod/Test]
        POSTGRES[PostgreSQL<br/>Prod/Test]
        MYDB[MySQL<br/>Prod/Test]
    end
    
    subgraph "LAYER 5 - Governance"
        SIEM[SIEM / Audit]
        SECRETS[Secret Manager]
    end
    
    DBA --> CLIENT
    CLIENT --> LLM
    CLIENT -.-> SQLCL
    CLIENT -.-> MSSQL
    CLIENT -.-> PG
    CLIENT -.-> MYSQL
    SQLCL --> ORACLE
    MSSQL --> SQLSERV
    PG --> POSTGRES
    MYSQL --> MYDB
    SQLCL -.-> SECRETS
    MSSQL -.-> SECRETS
    PG -.-> SECRETS
    SQLCL -.-> SIEM
    MSSQL -.-> SIEM
    PG -.-> SIEM
```
